  "id": "valve-stem-play-determine-A26D1C",
  "title": "Valve stem play, determine",
  "htmlContent": "<div class=\"content\">\n\r\n<table width=\"100%\" >\r\n  <!--XPRINT-->\r\n  <table>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td></td>\r\n   <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\r\n  \t\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  \r\n  <!--/XPRINT-->\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td >\n<p class=\"title\">Valve stem play, determine</p>\n\n<p>Special service tools required:</p>\n\n<p>MKM-6216, MKM-6216-200/300/400, Micrometer Screw</p>\n\n<p><span class=\"gt-notice\">Note:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> The\nengine-specific values can be found in the corresponding \"Technical\nData\".</p>\n\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95%\">\n<p><span class=\"gt-notice\">Note:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> The components\nof the dial gauge must be assembled according to the following\ninstructions.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/data/assets/images/1e33bc0b1f5e.gif\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"gt-picto\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Assemble</span></p>\n\n<p>Insert extension (3) in holder (2) and fasten. Insert internal\ncaliper (4) in extension and fasten. Attach holder with extension\nand internal caliper to the dial gauge (1) with approx. 1 mm\npretension and fasten. Fit calibration disc (5) for adjusting the\ndial gauge onto the internal caliper. Adjust dial gauge to Zero by\nturning dial. Carefully remove calibration disc.</p>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" align=\"right\"><!--SCDS Link: L6697.itf-->\n<img border=\"0\" width=\"360\" height=\"715\" alt=\n\"Object Number: 2418486  Size: DEFAULT\" align=\"TOP\" src=\"/data/assets/images/22c6cbdf0888.jpg\">\n<br>\n<a href=\"javascript:TFormSubmit('A0FL1SYK1PXK1','1','A0FL1SYK1PXK1','detail')\">\n<img src=\"/data/assets/images/db1138827f57.gif\" alt=\n\"Click here for detailed picture of above image\"></a>\n\n<br> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95%\">\n<p><img src=\"/data/assets/images/707731fa677f.gif\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"gt-picto\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Measure</span></p>\n\n<p>Determine inner diameter of valve guide at three different\nlevels, note values. Calculate mean value.</p>\n\n<p>Calculation example:</p>\n\n<p class=\"para-before-table\">Inner diameter of valve guide:</p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" class=\"border-none\">\n<colgroup>\n<col width=\"33%\" align=\"left\">\n<col width=\"27%\" align=\"left\">\n<col width=\"14%\" align=\"left\">\n<col width=\"26%\" align=\"left\"></colgroup>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Measurement I</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>7.025 mm</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Measurement II</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>7.030 mm</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-bot\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Measurement III</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-bot\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>7.020 mm</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"border-bot\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>21.075 mm</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>: 3 =</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-bot\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>7.025 mm</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n \n\n<p>Mean value = 7.025</p>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" align=\"right\"><!--SCDS Link: L6705.itf-->\n<img border=\"0\" width=\"360\" height=\"360\" alt=\n\"Object Number: 2418494  Size: DEFAULT\" align=\"TOP\" src=\"/data/assets/images/6bca28e792af.jpg\">\n<br>\n<a href=\"javascript:TFormSubmit('A1GL1XTK1YTK1','1','A1GL1XTK1YTK1','detail')\">\n<img src=\"/data/assets/images/db1138827f57.gif\" alt=\n\"Click here for detailed picture of above image\"></a>\n\n<br> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95%\">\n<p><img src=\"/data/assets/images/707731fa677f.gif\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"gt-picto\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Measure</span></p>\n\n<p>Determine valve stem diameter on cleaned valve using micrometer\nscrew, note value.</p>\n\n<p>The valve stem play can only be determined by calculation.</p>\n\n<p class=\"para-before-table\">Calculation example:</p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" class=\"border-none\">\n<colgroup>\n<col width=\"69%\" align=\"left\">\n<col width=\"31%\" align=\"left\"></colgroup>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Mean value of valve guide inner diameter</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"right\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>7.025 mm</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-bot\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Valve stem diameter</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-bot\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"right\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>-7.000 mm</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Gives a mean valve stem play of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"right\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>= 0.025 mm</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n \n\n<p>The difference between the mean inner diameter of the valve\nguide (7.025 mm) and the outer diameter of the valve stem (7.000\nmm) gives a mean valve stem play of (0.025 mm).</p>\n\n<p>The permissible valve stem play is found in the \"Technical\nData\".</p>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" align=\"right\"><!--SCDS Link: L6698.itf-->\n<img border=\"0\" width=\"360\" height=\"360\" alt=\n\"Object Number: 2418487  Size: DEFAULT\" align=\"TOP\" src=\"/data/assets/images/1c86e250f7d7.jpg\">\n<br>\n<a href=\"javascript:TFormSubmit('A8ML1Y0L19VK1','1','A8ML1Y0L19VK1','detail')\">\n<img src=\"/data/assets/images/db1138827f57.gif\" alt=\n\"Click here for detailed picture of above image\"></a>\n\n<br> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<p class=\"topic\">Procedure</p>\n\n<p>If the tolerances are exceeded, the valve guides must be reamed\nand the appropriate oversize valves installed.</p>\n\n<p>The specified values can be found in the \"Technical Data\".</p>\n</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  \r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td ></td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>",
